{
  "stem": "17001.7",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I figured it out the best thing is if I climb through the-- because it was divided.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I climb through.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I will place the potatoes on top of the extreme, which was frozen anyway.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So it wasn't that it was fresh.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when the Zahlappell comes, I won't have potatoes on me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So it was-- it was-- it was much earlier than usually, we had the Zahlappell.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We all go out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they made us kneel down.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were kneeling on-- on our knees, and they counting and counting and counting and counting.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Nobody is missing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[BACKGROUND NOISE] Meantime, to get back to this girl whom the German had caught, they were beating her to such an extent that she made a ciss under herself.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then one of the [GERMAN], after she beat her, she says to her, why did you steal?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Why did you have the nerve to go out, and how did you go out?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She said, I didn't go out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was left out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was hiding all-- all-- all night long.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She didn't want to say that-- how she went out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So the German [GERMAN] says that being that you don't want to snitch on the other people-- because don't tell me-- you didn't do this alone.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I'm going to bring you some soup.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She went to the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She brought soup for her.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "When-- when I came back and my sister told me what happened, I said, they are crazier than we are.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "First, she beats her to-- almost to death.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Then she brings her a plate of soup.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were in Nuremberg from November till March, which about four-- good four months.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But in that four months, we were going through a lot of bombing, a lot of suffering.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
